#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.4"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.4:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.4:0.2"
msgid "1. Ānisaṃsavagga"
msgstr "1. Benefits"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.4:0.3"
msgid "4. Dutiyaupanisasutta"
msgstr "4. Vital Conditions (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.4:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi … pe …"
msgstr "There Venerable Sāriputta addressed the mendicants …"

msgctxt "an10.4:1.2"
msgid "“dussīlassa, āvuso, sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti avippaṭisāro;"
msgstr ""
"“Reverends, an unethical person, who lacks ethics, has destroyed a vital "
"condition for having no regrets."

msgctxt "an10.4:1.3"
msgid "avippaṭisāre asati avippaṭisāravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"When there are regrets, one who has regrets has destroyed a vital condition "
"for joy. …"

msgctxt "an10.4:1.4"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"One who lacks disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition "
"for knowledge and vision of freedom."

msgctxt "an10.4:1.5"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, āvuso, rukkho sākhāpalāsavipanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi na pāripūriṃ "
"gacchati, tacopi … pheggupi … sāropi na pāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a tree that lacked branches and foliage. Its shoots, bark, "
"softwood, and heartwood would not grow to fullness."

msgctxt "an10.4:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, āvuso, dussīlassa sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti avippaṭisāro;"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, an unethical person, who lacks ethics, has destroyed a "
"vital condition for having no regrets."

msgctxt "an10.4:1.7"
msgid "avippaṭisāre asati avippaṭisāravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"When there are regrets, one who has regrets has destroyed a vital condition "
"for joy. …"

msgctxt "an10.4:1.8"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"One who lacks disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition "
"for knowledge and vision of freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.4:2.1"
msgid "Sīlavato, āvuso, sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti avippaṭisāro;"
msgstr ""
"An ethical person, who has fulfilled ethics, has fulfilled a vital condition "
"for not having regrets."

msgctxt "an10.4:2.2"
msgid "avippaṭisāre sati avippaṭisārasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"When there are no regrets, one who has no regrets has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for joy. …"

msgctxt "an10.4:2.3"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
msgstr ""
"One who has fulfilled disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for knowledge and vision of freedom."

msgctxt "an10.4:2.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, āvuso, rukkho sākhāpalāsasampanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi pāripūriṃ "
"gacchati, tacopi … pheggupi … sāropi pāripūriṃ gacchati."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a tree that was complete with branches and foliage. Its "
"shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would grow to fullness."

msgctxt "an10.4:2.5"
msgid ""
"Evamevaṃ kho, āvuso, sīlavato sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti "
"avippaṭisāro;"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, an ethical person, who has fulfilled ethics, has fulfilled "
"a vital condition for not having regrets."

msgctxt "an10.4:2.6"
msgid "avippaṭisāre sati avippaṭisārasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"When there are no regrets, one who has no regrets has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for joy. …"

msgctxt "an10.4:2.7"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanan”ti."
msgstr ""
"One who has fulfilled disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital "
"condition for knowledge and vision of freedom.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.4:2.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ."
msgstr ""
